		LoadingTips: {
			Tip1: Wizarding World: Craft an Enchanting Table to begin your magical journey!
			Tip2: Wizarding World: The wand chooses the wizard — try different wands for different spells.
			Tip3: Wizarding World: Visit the Forbidden Forest at night for unique magical creatures.
			Tip4: Wizarding World: Collect Essence of Magic from magical creatures for advanced crafting.
			Tip5: Wizarding World: Defeat the Basilisk, Hungarian Horntail, and Lord Voldemort!
			Tip6: Wizarding World: Buy the Standard Book of Spells from Ollivander for a complete guide.
			Tip7: Wizarding World: Each Hogwarts house armor has a matching signature weapon.
			Tip8: Wizarding World: Unicorn Blood only drops in the Forbidden Forest — a rare treasure.
			Tip9: Wizarding World: Check the Daily Prophet for today's Wizard Challenge — earn bonus Essence!
			Tip10: Wizarding World: The Wizard's Almanac (sold by Dumbledore) is a 10-page encyclopedia of the entire mod.
		}

