		DiagonAlley: {
			Welcome: You tap the wall behind the Leaky Cauldron... the bricks rearrange themselves, and Diagon Alley opens before you!
			StreetDescription: The cobblestone street stretches ahead, lined with magical shopfronts and bustling with wizards.
			Gringotts: "  GRINGOTTS BANK -- the white marble building towers ahead. Speak to the Goblin Teller for vault contracts."
			Ollivanders: "  OLLIVANDERS -- Fine Wands since 382 B.C. The best wands choose their wizard here."
			Wheezes: "  WEASLEYS' WIZARD WHEEZES -- Fred and George's joke shop blazes with colour and noise."
			SourceVisit: Diagon Alley visit
			CartDescent1: The goblin leads you to a cart on iron rails. 'Vault access authorized. Hold on.'
			CartDescent2: The cart lurches forward, descending deep beneath London. Torches blur past.
			CartDescent3: With a screech of brakes, the cart stops. 'Your vault. Touch nothing that is not yours.'
		}

