		Forest: {
			Entered: You step beneath the shadowed boughs of the Forbidden Forest.
			Exited: You leave the Forbidden Forest behind.
			EnteredPostHorntail: Charred tracks cut through the undergrowth. Larger beasts are awake.
			EnteredPostVoldemort: The forest remembers the war. The air is still watching.
			Unlocked: The Forbidden Forest opens its deeper paths. Hagrid's expeditions are now available.
			HagridBriefing: Use the Forest Expedition Lantern at night in the Forbidden Forest to begin a mission.
			UnicornGladeStart: UNICORN GLADE -- Dark corrupted traces have appeared. Cleanse them to restore the glade's purity.
			SkywatchStart: CENTAUR SKYWATCH -- Unstable omen stones are disrupting celestial readings. Stabilize them.
			NestStart: ACROMANTULA NEST -- Brood markers are spawning spiders. Destroy them to clear the den.
			CompleteObjectives: Destroy {0} objectives before time runs out.
			ObjectiveProgress: Objectives completed: {0}/{1}
			TimeWarning: 30 seconds remaining! The forest grows restless!
			UnicornGladeComplete: The corrupted traces are cleansed. The Unicorn Glade shimmers with restored purity.
			SkywatchComplete: The omen stones are stabilized. The centaurs can read the stars once more.
			NestComplete: The brood markers are destroyed. The spider den falls silent.
			MissionFailed: Time expired. The forest reclaims its secrets.
			NotUnlocked: The deeper forest paths are sealed. Defeat the Basilisk first.
			ActiveStatus: Expedition active: {0}/{1} objectives, {2} seconds remaining.
			ReadyStatus: Expeditions completed: {0}. Next mission: {1}.
			SourceExpedition: Forest expedition
			ExpeditionButton: Expedition Status
			ThestralStart: THESTRAL CLEARING -- Moonlit beacons have appeared in the clearing. Activate them to stabilize the spectral energy.
			ThestralComplete: The beacons are stabilized. The Thestral Clearing glows softly with moonlit tranquility.
			HagridExpedition1: Right then! The forest needs our help. Take this lantern and head in after dark.
			HagridExpedition2: The Unicorn Glade's been tainted -- dark traces, not the unicorns themselves. We protect them, we don't hunt them.
			HagridExpedition3: The centaurs are worried about their star readings. Unstable omen stones, they say.
			HagridExpedition4: Aragog's old colony has gone wild. Brood markers keepin' them organized. Smash those and they'll scatter.
			HagridExpedition5: Yeh've done good work in there. The forest remembers those who help it.
			HagridExpedition6: There's a clearing deeper in the forest where Thestrals gather. Beautiful creatures, really. Only those who've seen death can see 'em.
		}

