			Description: The safehouse needs constant upkeep against infestations, cursed portraits, and dark creatures.
			DoxySweepStart: DOXY SWEEP -- The house is buzzing with Doxy nests. Destroy them before they breed out of control!
			PortraitStart: PORTRAIT SUPPRESSION -- Walburga's portrait is shrieking again. Silence the cursed frames!
			BoggartStart: BOGGART WARD -- Fear manifestations have taken root. Banish them -- Riddikulus is most effective!
