			PortraitComplete: Walburga's portrait falls silent at last. The shrieking has stopped.
			BoggartComplete: The Boggart dissolves into mist! The wardrobe is clear.
			MissionFailed: The safehouse has been overwhelmed. The wards have sealed it again.
