		SceneEffects: {
			AzkabanOppression: The air grows cold. Despair seeps from the walls.
			MysteryProphecy: Whispers of fate echo through the Hall of Prophecy.
			MysteryTime: Time bends here. The air shimmers with temporal distortion.
			MysteryDeath: The Veil calls. Stay back from the arch.
			GrimmauldHostile: Dark objects stir. The Black family's legacy persists.
			StMungosWard: Magical maladies fill the air. Caution is advised.
			BattleSiege: The castle shakes under the assault. Hold the line.
			DiagonBustle: The magical bustle of Diagon Alley surrounds you.
			KnockturnShadow: Shadows deepen in Knockturn Alley. Watch your step.
			GringottsDepth: Deep beneath London, the vaults of Gringotts await.
			ShriekingMoonlit: Moonlight pierces through the broken shutters. Something stirs.
			WillowDanger: The Whomping Willow lashes overhead. Stay low.
