		Transit: {
			PassageFade: The wall shimmers and a hidden passage appears...
			PassageTravel: You slip through the secret passage, footsteps echoing in the dark...
			PassageArrive: You emerge from the passage, dusting yourself off.
			HogsHeadEntry: Aberforth nods. The passage behind the portrait swings open.
			HogsHeadTravel: The winding tunnel stretches ahead, lit by distant wand-light.
			WillowEntry: The knot freezes. The Whomping Willow goes still. Quickly now...
			WillowTunnel: Low ceiling, damp earth. The passage narrows toward the Shack.
			GringottsDescend: The cart plunges downward. Torches blur past. Your stomach lurches.
