		BattleEndgame: {
			NaginiPhase: Nagini coils protectively! Strike now -- destroy the final Horcrux!
			NaginiStrike: Neville raises the Sword of Gryffindor! Nagini must fall!
			CastleDefenders: The castle's defenders rally! Animated armor marches to the front line.
			McGonagallRally: Professor McGonagall raises her wand: 'Piertotum Locomotor!' The castle's statues march to war.
			DefenderFlavor: Stone guardians patrol the corridors, shielding students from harm.
			SiegeIntensity: The castle trembles. Explosions of light and dark magic fill the sky.
		}

		DailyChallenge: {
			DefeatCreatures: Defeat 20 magical creatures
			DefeatForest: Defeat 10 enemies in the Forbidden Forest
			DefeatDarkForces: Defeat 5 Dementors or Death Eaters
			DefeatUnderground: Defeat 15 underground wizard creatures
			DefeatAny: Defeat 30 wizard enemies (any type)
			Status: Daily Challenge: {0} ({1}/{2})
			CompleteToday: Today's challenge is complete. Come back tomorrow.
			Complete: Daily wizard challenge complete. Essence of Magic rewarded!
		}

		HogwartsLetterEvent: {
			OwlArrives: An owl swoops down and drops a letter at your feet!
			Accepted: You've been accepted to the Wizarding World!
		}

		Renown: {
			Champion: HOUSE CHAMPION! Maximum renown achieved!
			MajorBuff: 150 House Renown! Major house buff activated!
			MinorBuff: 50 House Renown! Minor house buff activated!
		}

		Resurrection.RiseFromAshes: You rise from the ashes!

		BossDialogue: {
			QuirrellPhase2: The face beneath the turban stirs. Something far worse is waking.
			QuirrellPhase3: Voldemort's shadow takes control. Survive the final curse storm!
			UmbridgePhase2: Hem hem. Detention will now become permanent.
			UmbridgePhase3: Order! I will have order!
			UmbridgeSummon: The Inquisitorial Squad answers Umbridge's call!
			UmbridgeDecree: Educational Decree #{0}: {1} is now forbidden!
			BellatrixPhase2: Bellatrix cackles and vanishes into a storm of curses!
			BellatrixPhase3: She abandons restraint. The duel becomes pure madness.
			BellatrixTaunt1: I killed Sirius Black!
			BellatrixTaunt2: You dare duel me?
			BellatrixTaunt3: Crucio!
			BellatrixTaunt4: The Dark Lord will reward me for this!
			BellatrixSummon: Bellatrix calls dark allies from the shadows!
		}

		ClassQuest: {
			TaskComplete: Class task complete: {0}
			DADAMastery: Defense Against the Dark Arts mastery increased to {0}.
			PotionsMastery: Potions mastery increased to {0}.
			CreaturesMastery: Care of Magical Creatures mastery increased to {0}.
			CharmsMastery: Charms mastery increased to {0}.
		}

		Hallows: {
			GuidanceHorcruxes: Destroy the core Horcruxes before seeking the Hallows.
			GuidanceAzkaban: Azkaban's Despair must fall before the cloak can be entrusted.
			GuidanceCloak: Ask Dumbledore about the true Invisibility Cloak.
			GuidanceVoldemort: Voldemort still stands between you and the Stone.
			GuidanceRing: Bring Gaunt's Ring to Dumbledore when the war is won.
			GuidancePurify: The ring can be purified now. Do not wait.
			GuidanceUnite: Equip the Elder Wand, true Cloak, and Stone together.
			GuidanceComplete: The Hallows are united. Death has no master here.
			CloakReveal1: Dumbledore reveals the true Invisibility Cloak.
			CloakReveal2: It settles around you like a quiet promise.
			StoneReveal1: Gaunt's Ring cracks. The Resurrection Stone awakens.
			StoneReveal2: The dead do not return, but their courage remains.
			MasterOfDeath1: The Deathly Hallows answer as one.
			MasterOfDeath2: You are the Master of Death.
			MasterOfDeath3: Fate bends, but it does not break.
			DeathRespite: The Hallows pull you back from the edge of death.
			DespairMedium: "{0} presses against your thoughts."
			DespairHigh: Despair closes in. Hold to your Patronus.
			DespairCritical: The darkness is almost complete.
		}
	}
}

